{"tid":1407554,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"黃大仙有野想同各位講D野","createTime":"2019-08-04T15:38:01.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-04T17:57:11.000Z","uid":260616,"like":160,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":21,"replies":[{"pid":"c0adabc0ce20b4a2c9e563ed0c9b79b9a6763340","tid":1407554,"uid":260616,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T15:38:01.000Z","msg":"琴日發夢，黃大仙同我講，叫人去黃大仙求簽<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">黃大仙</span></span>是一個好L正的地方<br />\n第一，去九西同荃葵青都要經龍翔道，獅子山其中一個入口都係要由龍翔轉入去<br />\n九東同港島東要去獅隧都要龍翔入去，所以是好好好好好好好<span style=\"color: red;\">重要</span>～～&middot;<br />\n<br />\n第二，龍翔道附近好多市民居住的地方，如果班狗射催淚彈，打人，開槍，有好多市民都會受到影響，同埋睇L住班狗，知道班狗有幾衰，到時民意會好容易企我地呢邊。<br />\n<br />\n第三，黃大仙附近的地至複雜，有好多位卑義士走 or 轉場：<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/YhRi7tm.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FYhRi7tm.png&h=62d953f4&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n可以走去慈雲山，樂富，鑽石山，或者求簽！<br />\n<br />\n希望大家＋油！"},{"pid":"46bbc27e93cb39831b54c78080c3244d9ab30c19","tid":1407554,"uid":260616,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T15:38:11.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"ff57aa615ea1650cd39f3c8734088722321e20d5","tid":1407554,"uid":260616,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T15:38:22.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"4487c9aade9b98eba5cee274a47eb6c2a9eddac2","tid":1407554,"uid":260616,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T15:38:32.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"d3344120bbe4116aa163f819893389ade365011b","tid":1407554,"uid":260616,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T15:38:42.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"3d27fe7d914960a0ad1fa3ca1c00016171e1f405","tid":1407554,"uid":101226,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T15:38:47.000Z","msg":"黃大仙人幫推"},{"pid":"ecd8259a61c054485e0fce6478217c5f93ea6e25","tid":1407554,"uid":260616,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T15:38:52.000Z","msg":"推"},{"p